{"tid":1392753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果今鋪我地贏左","createTime":"2019-08-01T00:23:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T00:52:16.000Z","uid":282328,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7b5d3076681bc2916c072b48d5438cf5417e53b2","tid":1392753,"uid":282328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:23:22.000Z","msg":"不如攪個勝利集會 雖然個名好柒 好想攬下大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">撐住呀手足！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n#光復香港<br />\n#時代革命"},{"pid":"e472faa2b687b8bab7fba91feda17e86455100b7","tid":1392753,"uid":106291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:26:25.000Z","msg":"點先叫贏"},{"pid":"180890b4712d1f429e8f2bba3bf97cddf86fa862","tid":1392753,"uid":282328,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e472faa2b687b8bab7fba91feda17e86455100b7","tid":1392753,"uid":106291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:26:25.000Z","msg":"點先叫贏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:31:30.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一𣎴可<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ac7990a42cb97ddedc31f37c1c4ebd280029517","tid":1392753,"uid":6528,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:36:19.000Z","msg":"全民8月5日大罷工！五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙普選一定要排最頭，仲要好似美國咁設時限係2020年內落實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n當新移民夠多，雙普選自然會落實，港共明顯會用偽民主反真港人<br />\n（雖然係舊post，但都想人諗下，一定要止左血先）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1328467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1328467</a><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港獨立</span>呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以好似上一代咁，計好哂數50年後都死左啦，唔好理啦。<br />\n我地唔可以再咁自私啦，過埋2047都嗰頭近啦，之後再算啦。<br />\n我想我地既下一代唔需要再為呢啲事再受苦啦，我只係希望下一代可以係呼吸住自由既空氣出世係呢個地球上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有既問題，所有既恩怨，係我地呢代到解決哂啦，好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭，仲要設時限，最好2020年內！"},{"pid":"841dd1c24793a00f4a7aee3c798a5a15817250df","tid":1392753,"uid":232370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:37:37.000Z","msg":"贏乜Q 有排都唔好諗<br />\n極權政府點會咁收手"},{"pid":"30aa94513b450e4a3b61753ead9cf8a468630f99","tid":1392753,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:38:22.000Z","msg":"歷史上唔會有大愛爭取到民主<br />\n<br />\n一定要佢地輸, 人民先有得贏"},{"pid":"15dcda93cef5fa2cd4d9e0f004d5ad3eeb65b3d3","tid":1392753,"uid":73400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:45:17.000Z","msg":"2019 逆權公民!!!"},{"pid":"30fac50faa1073f14c9cd05b7ed03f543dac8d4d","tid":1392753,"uid":129130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:52:16.000Z","msg":"贏咗你想點都得㗎啦"}]}